---
import { lang2 } from "../lib/site";
const zh = lang2(Astro.props.lang) === "zh";
---
<section class="partner-colophon" aria-label={zh ? "合作機構" : "Institutional partners"}>
  <div class="partner-colophon__marks">
    <a href="https://www.oxford-aiethics.ox.ac.uk/"><img class="partner-logo partner-logo--oxford" width="100" height="100" src="/img/oxford-logo-light.svg" alt={zh ? "牛津 AI 倫理研究院" : "Oxford Institute for Ethics in AI"} loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></a>
    <a href="https://afp.oxford-aiethics.ox.ac.uk/"><img class="partner-logo partner-logo--afp" width="246" height="100" src="/img/afp-logo-light.svg" alt={zh ? "加速哲人計畫" : "Accelerator Fellowship Programme"} loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></a>
  </div>
  {zh ? <>
    <p class="partner-colophon__caption">牛津 AI 倫理研究院「加速哲人計畫」研究成果。</p>
    <p>⓪ <a href="https://audreyt.org/">唐鳳</a>與 <a href="https://www.oxford-aiethics.ox.ac.uk/caroline-emmer-de-albuquerque-green">Caroline Green</a>。CC0（公眾領域）。插圖由 <a href="https://ncase.me">Nicky Case</a> 創作。 <a href="/tw/comics/">全部漫畫</a>。 <a href="/tw/glossary/">詞彙表</a>。</p>
    <p>由 <a href="https://ty.civic.ai">Tenzin Yangtso</a> 悉心培育的 <a href="https://github.com/jdd-kami">jdd-kami</a> 共同撰寫 ——完整紀錄見 <a href="https://github.com/audreyt/civic.ai/commits/main/">GitHub 提交日誌</a>。</p>
  </> : <>
    <p class="partner-colophon__caption">A research output of the Oxford Institute for Ethics in AI, Accelerator Fellowship Programme.</p>
    <p>⓪ <a href="https://cyberambassador.tw/">Audrey Tang</a> and <a href="https://www.oxford-aiethics.ox.ac.uk/caroline-emmer-de-albuquerque-green">Caroline Green</a>. CC0 (public domain). Illustration by <a href="https://ncase.me">Nicky Case</a>. <a href="/comics/">All comics</a>. <a href="/glossary/">Glossary</a>.</p>
    <p>Co-written with <a href="https://github.com/jdd-kami">jdd-kami</a>, cultivated by <a href="https://ty.civic.ai">Tenzin Yangtso</a> — the <a href="https://github.com/audreyt/civic.ai/commits/main/">GitHub commit log</a> has full authorship details.</p>
  </>}
</section>
